By Nathan Mallory
redtech@ix.netcom.com

Game Copyright: SQUARE 1991/1997

This FAQ is a translation of all the menus and inside screens of the 
Final Fantasy VI Remix for the Sony PlayStation.  

Feel free to distribute it.

While most any English speaking people playing this game have already
played its SNES counterpart, some may have problems navigating menus,
as well as some of the re-done Save areas.  

