IV.  EQUIP
Here you can put on your various equipment onto the following parts of your body (listed from 
Top to Bottom):
     -Right Hand
     -Left Hand
     -Head
     -Body
     -Hands

Also at the bottom left it says if the person is Right-Handed or
Left-Handed.  If there are 4
characters, the person is Right-Handed.  
If there are 5 characters, they are Left-Handed.
